3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of neural networks for 3D pose estimation can also be considered as an application of artificial intelligence, making cs.AI a likely sub-category.
4. cs.GR (Graphics): The paper deals with 3D human pose estimation, which is related to computer graphics. Therefore, cs.GR is also a possible sub-category.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia): The proposed algorithm can be used for multimedia applications such as motion capture and animation. Therefore, cs.MM is also a possible sub-category.
